('95984','33111','5','Charming Villa in Golf Resort Abubillas, Santa Ponsa'),
('95985','33112','5','The well maintained villa exudes a particularly pronounced Mediterranean charm and is in 1st line golf course on an approximately 625m² of land. From all levels you have a wonderful view in the south orientation overlooking the golf course of Santa Ponsa I. The villa complex Abubillas was created late 90s by star designer Pedro Otzup and enjoys still great popularity today. Abubillas is a place for relaxation, not only for golfers who spend part of the year here, but also for residents who live here all year round. The villa offers approximately 220m² of living space, which is distributed as follows: The ground floor entrance hall, living-dining room with high ceilings, open kitchen with wet bar, guest toilet, 2 bedrooms with a bathroom en suite. An outside staircase leads to the 1st floor to a guest bedroom with bathroom en suite and large terrace. The Mediterranean garden is watered automatically. A 4x8m large pool with counter current system and a roofed lounge area with fireplace and sauna invite you to relax. Is well equipped with air conditioning w / c, electric., underfloor heating in the bathrooms, fitted kitchen, fireplace in living room, and more'),
